#, no-c-format
msgid "Originally developed by &Matthias.Elter; &Matthias.Elter.mail;"
msgstr "मूल रूप से &Matthias.Elter; &Matthias.Elter.mail; द्वारा विकसित"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:852
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The current maintainer is &Cornelius.Schumacher; &Cornelius.Schumacher.mail;"
msgstr "वर्तमान अनुरक्षक &Cornelius.Schumacher; &Cornelius.Schumacher.mail; है"

